Elaine Taylor (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elaine_Taylor_(actress) 0 Elaine Regina Taylor (born 17 October 1943) is an English actress, best known as a leading lady in comedy films of the late 1960s and early 1970s. She is married to the Canadian actor Christopher Plummer.
